[03/12/2018 15:53:40] <font color="#ffffff">A Mael.</font>
[03/12/2018 15:53:40] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Un agujero?</font>
[03/12/2018 15:53:41] <font color="#00ff00">¡Un agujero, claro!</font>
